---
description: API routes — REST endpoints, image proxy, video webhook, fal proxy
globs:
  - src/app/api/**
---

API route conventions:
- Image proxy: `src/app/api/images/[...filePath]/route.ts` — stream files with `createReadStream`
- Fal proxy: `/api/fal/proxy` — proxies requests to Fal.ai
- Video webhook: `/api/video/webhook/route.ts` — verify signatures via `src/lib/webhook-verification.ts`
- V1 API: `/api/v1/` — external API with CORS headers (see `middleware.ts`)
- `cookies()` and `headers()` are async — always `await`
- Every `fetch()` needs explicit `cache:` option
